<section class="policy-body">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="policy-text">

      <p>We want everything to fit like it was made for you. Our pieces are designed to be relaxed but flattering — if you're between sizes, we recommend sizing down for a more fitted look or staying true for a breezier drape.</p>

      <h2>Dresses & Tops</h2>
      <div class="size-table-wrap">
        <table class="size-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Size</th><th>Bust</th><th>Waist</th><th>Hips</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>XS</td><td>31–33"</td><td>24–26"</td><td>34–36"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>S</td><td>33–35"</td><td>26–28"</td><td>36–38"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>M</td><td>35–37"</td><td>28–30"</td><td>38–40"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>L</td><td>37–40"</td><td>30–33"</td><td>40–43"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>XL</td><td>40–43"</td><td>33–36"</td><td>43–46"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>2X</td><td>43–46"</td><td>36–39"</td><td>46–49"</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <h2>Shorts & Bottoms</h2>
      <div class="size-table-wrap">
        <table class="size-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Size</th><th>Waist</th><th>Hips</th><th>Inseam</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>XS</td><td>24–26"</td><td>34–36"</td><td>3–4"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>S</td><td>26–28"</td><td>36–38"</td><td>3–4"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>M</td><td>28–30"</td><td>38–40"</td><td>4"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>L</td><td>30–33"</td><td>40–43"</td><td>4"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>XL</td><td>33–36"</td><td>43–46"</td><td>4–5"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>2X</td><td>36–39"</td><td>46–49"</td><td>4–5"</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <h2>Swim</h2>
      <div class="size-table-wrap">
        <table class="size-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Size</th><th>Bust</th><th>Waist</th><th>Hips</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>XS</td><td>30–32"</td><td>24–25"</td><td>34–35"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>S</td><td>32–34"</td><td>25–27"</td><td>35–37"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>M</td><td>34–36"</td><td>27–29"</td><td>37–39"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>L</td><td>36–39"</td><td>29–32"</td><td>39–42"</td></tr>
            <tr><td>XL</td><td>39–42"</td><td>32–35"</td><td>42–45"</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <h2>How to Measure</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Bust:</strong> Measure around the fullest part of your chest, keeping the tape level</li>
        <li><strong>Waist:</strong> Measure at your natural waistline — the narrowest part of your torso</li>
        <li><strong>Hips:</strong> Measure around the fullest part of your hips</li>
        <li><strong>Inseam:</strong> Measure from your inner thigh to where you'd like the shorts to end</li>
      </ul>

      <hr>

      <h2>Still not sure?</h2>
      <p>Try our <strong>AI Try-On</strong> — upload a photo and see how any piece looks on you before you buy. Or email us at <a href="mailto:support@coastalpalm.shop">support@coastalpalm.shop</a> with your measurements and we'll help you find the right fit.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

